20
00:00:58,094 --> 00:01:03,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Intense days go by.
(But you know)</b></font>

21
00:01:03,114 --> 00:01:07,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just laugh it off, because it's a game worth competing.</b></font>

22
00:01:07,814 --> 00:01:10,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's see how fast you can do it.</b></font>

23
00:01:10,344 --> 00:01:15,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Raise up your hands forever.
(Everybody now raise your hands up)</b></font>

24
00:01:15,164 --> 00:01:19,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Run, sleepless challenger.
(You don't stop)</b></font>

25
00:01:19,394 --> 00:01:21,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a quest of the never ending dream</b></font>

26
00:01:21,854 --> 00:01:26,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>where you now search for the reason to live.
(Let's go)</b></font>

27
00:01:26,014 --> 00:01:27,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh
(Let's go)</b></font>

28
00:01:27,064 --> 00:01:30,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, raise up your hands now.</b></font>

29
00:01:54,664 --> 00:01:55,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here they come!</b></font>

30
00:02:08,794 --> 00:02:11,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why? What made them so excited?</b></font>

31
00:02:12,414 --> 00:02:13,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's your take, Mako?</b></font>

32
00:02:13,874 --> 00:02:18,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hard to say, but at the least 
the NSX's traction is impressive.</b></font>

33
00:02:18,914 --> 00:02:24,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The exit of this corner is really steep, but it 
accelerated quickly without losing balance.</b></font>

34
00:02:25,714 --> 00:02:28,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The FD is at a disadvantage after all, 
because its response was one step behind.</b></font>

35
00:02:31,314 --> 00:02:35,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hojo's red car wasn't having fun.</b></font>

36
00:02:35,214 --> 00:02:39,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But the yellow car was smiling.</b></font>

37
00:02:42,914 --> 00:02:47,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I knew early on that our
opponent would be using an NSX.</b></font>

38
00:02:47,564 --> 00:02:51,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not like Keisuke and I just 
sat back and waited for today.</b></font>

39
00:02:52,364 --> 00:02:54,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have our own trump card.</b></font>

40
00:02:57,714 --> 00:03:01,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They passed the hairpin at the observatory, and have entered section 4.</b></font>

41
00:03:02,164 --> 00:03:03,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>From there...</b></font>

42
00:03:08,614 --> 00:03:09,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's begun.</b></font>

43
00:03:10,724 --> 00:03:15,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't conserve the tires from here on, but I'm counting on you, my FD.</b></font>

44
00:03:15,164 --> 00:03:16,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please hold on.</b></font>

45
00:03:52,914 --> 00:03:57,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's so frustrating!
How is the battle going?!</b></font>

46
00:03:57,594 --> 00:03:59,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Calm down, Itsuki.</b></font>

47
00:03:59,394 --> 00:04:02,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I'm so worried 
that I can't stand still!</b></font>

48
00:04:03,424 --> 00:04:06,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're probably maintaining
their positions at the moment.</b></font>

49
00:04:06,914 --> 00:04:11,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The NSX tries to flee while
the FD tries to catch it.</b></font>

50
00:04:11,164 --> 00:04:12,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right.</b></font>

51
00:04:12,134 --> 00:04:15,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But do you really think the FD can win?</b></font>

52
00:04:17,664 --> 00:04:19,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you saying, Kenji?</b></font>

53
00:04:19,984 --> 00:04:22,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You saw it, didn't you?</b></font>

54
00:04:22,264 --> 00:04:26,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That speed was incomparable.
Besides, it's in the lead position.</b></font>

55
00:04:26,084 --> 00:04:31,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takahashi Keisuke will win no matter what 
because he's Project D's ace in the hill climb!</b></font>

56
00:04:31,964 --> 00:04:33,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Same for Takumi.</b></font>

57
00:04:42,094 --> 00:04:44,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're in section 4.</b></font>

58
00:04:44,264 --> 00:04:47,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Everything has gone as planned so far.</b></font>

59
00:04:47,014 --> 00:04:49,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The real battle begins now.</b></font>

60
00:05:01,964 --> 00:05:06,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Act 13  [ Battle Beyond Expectations ]</b></font>

61
00:05:10,484 --> 00:05:14,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Matsumoto, I couldn't tell you this until now</b></font>

62
00:05:14,264 --> 00:05:18,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I hesitated to pick Keisuke
as a driver for Project D.</b></font>

63
00:05:20,544 --> 00:05:27,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There was a time when he looked inferior, when
compared to Fujiwara with his splendid talent.</b></font>

64
00:05:27,254 --> 00:05:30,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke must have felt it,
more or less, as well.</b></font>

65
00:05:31,574 --> 00:05:34,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Drivers naturally figure those things out.</b></font>

66
00:05:37,984 --> 00:05:41,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He must have felt a certain degree of pressure.</b></font>

67
00:05:41,344 --> 00:05:47,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As for me, I didn't want to
favor my blood related brother.</b></font>

68
00:05:47,854 --> 00:05:50,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why I've been trying to distance myself from him, and acted harshly.</b></font>

69
00:05:52,154 --> 00:05:53,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, you have.</b></font>

70
00:05:53,914 --> 00:06:02,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I remember when Keisuke damaged his car's suspension after going through some oil during our Saitama expeditionary race.</b></font>

71
00:06:31,714 --> 00:06:32,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dammit!</b></font>

72
00:06:33,914 --> 00:06:36,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This pisses me off!</b></font>

73
00:06:36,054 --> 00:06:38,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You have no time to vent 
your frustration on the guardrail.</b></font>

74
00:06:39,914 --> 00:06:43,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's your fault that your FD was damaged.</b></font>

75
00:06:45,164 --> 00:06:46,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My fault?</b></font>

76
00:06:46,154 --> 00:06:51,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. I wouldn't have damaged 
my car because of a trap like this.</b></font>

77
00:06:51,984 --> 00:06:54,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your overconfidence and
carelessness brought you to this.</b></font>

78
00:06:54,964 --> 00:06:56,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Calm down and think.</b></font>

79
00:07:03,354 --> 00:07:10,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You blamed Keisuke for his carelessness, instead of our opponent's dirty trick.</b></font>

80
00:07:11,314 --> 00:07:13,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I felt sorry for him.</b></font>

81
00:07:14,114 --> 00:07:17,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's been pretty tough since he was little.</b></font>

82
00:07:17,314 --> 00:07:21,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He improves more from getting 
chewed out than from receiving praise.</b></font>

83
00:07:21,394 --> 00:07:25,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was around that time when the
look in his eyes began to change.</b></font>

84
00:07:26,974 --> 00:07:34,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Regarding the training of having Keisuke match a preset time, I was obsessed with the same training a long time ago.</b></font>

85
00:07:36,254 --> 00:07:40,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Surprisingly, you don't learn much when you're desperate and trying to drive fast.</b></font>

86
00:07:40,734 --> 00:07:44,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your concentration doesn't last,
and you'll only put stress your car.</b></font>

87
00:07:49,364 --> 00:07:55,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But you think hard and discover 
more by practicing car control.</b></font>

88
00:07:58,834 --> 00:08:02,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can reach your limit only
 after you perfect such control.</b></font>

89
00:08:04,314 --> 00:08:05,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got the section time.</b></font>

90
00:08:06,474 --> 00:08:09,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's nearly Gou's best time.</b></font>

91
00:08:11,154 --> 00:08:15,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>None of the Sidewinder team 
members could keep up with this pace.</b></font>

92
00:08:15,664 --> 00:08:17,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takahashi Keisuke is the real thing.</b></font>

93
00:08:19,824 --> 00:08:25,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There are a lot of spectators, but not very
many of them truly understand what's going on.</b></font>

94
00:08:30,054 --> 00:08:33,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At a glance, the situation 
appears to be deadlocked</b></font>

95
00:08:33,314 --> 00:08:38,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but both drivers are managing
their tires extremely well.</b></font>

96
00:08:39,984 --> 00:08:44,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A high level race that appeals to
 the experts tends to look uneventful.</b></font>

97
00:08:46,044 --> 00:08:48,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara is a typical example.</b></font>

98
00:08:48,664 --> 00:08:51,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's a master of vehicle control.</b></font>

99
00:08:51,584 --> 00:08:53,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're right.</b></font>

100
00:08:53,824 --> 00:08:57,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You could say that Keisuke's sense 
of rivalry with Fujiwara improved him.</b></font>

101
00:08:59,044 --> 00:09:07,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whether it's heavy rain or fog, even when he was sick, he never skipped his driving training on Akagi roads.</b></font>

102
00:09:07,014 --> 00:09:11,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Some say a never ending passion
is what brilliance is all about</b></font>

103
00:09:11,714 --> 00:09:13,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and Keisuke has something like that.</b></font>

104
00:09:16,674 --> 00:09:21,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara and Keisuke are 
mutually beneficial to one another.</b></font>

105
00:09:21,464 --> 00:09:26,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To be honest, Matsumoto, this past month.</b></font>

106
00:09:26,554 --> 00:09:29,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Actually, in the past 
two weeks to be precise</b></font>

107
00:09:30,814 --> 00:09:34,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke has reached an incredible level.</b></font>

108
00:09:38,374 --> 00:09:39,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An incredible level?</b></font>

109
00:09:47,544 --> 00:09:50,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His time is dead accurate to the preset time.</b></font>

110
00:09:52,284 --> 00:09:58,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even when he faces obstacles that might 
disrupt his pace, he matches the time in the end.</b></font>

111
00:09:58,824 --> 00:10:03,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He must have developed 
an accurate internal clock.</b></font>

112
00:10:04,094 --> 00:10:08,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My past peak performance
wouldn't beat today's Keisuke.</b></font>

113
00:10:12,344 --> 00:10:17,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I did the same training, so I can
 understand how impressive he is.</b></font>

114
00:10:17,014 --> 00:10:24,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's godlike to drive such a long Akagi road 
within an error margin of less than 1 second.</b></font>

115
00:10:25,414 --> 00:10:30,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Many factors have contributed
 to Keisuke's breakthrough.</b></font>

116
00:10:31,114 --> 00:10:37,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My training method created
 an incredible street racer.</b></font>

117
00:10:37,054 --> 00:10:40,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His condition is extremely good.</b></font>

118
00:10:40,924 --> 00:10:42,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a pleasant surprise.</b></font>

119
00:10:43,984 --> 00:10:45,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We made it time for the final battle.</b></font>

120
00:10:49,114 --> 00:10:52,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our trump card is Keisuke himself.</b></font>

121
00:11:21,234 --> 00:11:25,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kogashiwa, what's your impression
of the NSX's performance?</b></font>

122
00:11:25,704 --> 00:11:30,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To me, it only looks like it's
 desperately trying to go fast.</b></font>

123
00:11:30,564 --> 00:11:34,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's going flat out, and 
the tires are at their limit.</b></font>

124
00:11:34,664 --> 00:11:37,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>More than anything, the lines
 show the driver's seriousness.</b></font>

125
00:11:37,974 --> 00:11:39,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I agree.</b></font>

126
00:11:40,204 --> 00:11:44,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then why is Takahashi 
Keisuke's FD right behind it?</b></font>

127
00:11:45,664 --> 00:11:47,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's going on?</b></font>

128
00:12:05,824 --> 00:12:08,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't what we discussed.</b></font>

129
00:12:09,774 --> 00:12:13,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your car should have
 a 15 second advantage.</b></font>

130
00:12:13,134 --> 00:12:16,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you have any qualms with
 only a 15 second advantage?</b></font>

131
00:12:16,174 --> 00:12:20,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's enough.
Who do you think I am, Kubo?</b></font>

132
00:12:20,294 --> 00:12:24,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you think I'll lose to some punk
from Gunma in driving technique?</b></font>

133
00:12:29,574 --> 00:12:30,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is really frustrating.</b></font>

134
00:12:41,564 --> 00:12:43,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dammit, this sucks.</b></font>

135
00:13:00,944 --> 00:13:04,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Slim, long and beautiful legs.</b></font>

136
00:13:08,484 --> 00:13:11,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And she gives off a nice scent.</b></font>

137
00:13:12,414 --> 00:13:15,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako is a mature woman.</b></font>

138
00:13:19,954 --> 00:13:23,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who would've anticipated a deadlock like this?</b></font>

139
00:13:23,524 --> 00:13:27,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is really unexpected,
but things are getting interesting.</b></font>

140
00:13:27,974 --> 00:13:31,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hojo Gou trying to settle
 the match, but he's failing.</b></font>

141
00:13:31,664 --> 00:13:34,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Project D is quite something indeed.</b></font>

142
00:13:35,134 --> 00:13:38,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's not much left 
after this hairpin curve.</b></font>

143
00:13:38,664 --> 00:13:43,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This must be a surprising
turn of events for Sidewinder.</b></font>

144
00:13:43,024 --> 00:13:47,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think they've prepared
 for a second or third run.</b></font>

145
00:13:48,464 --> 00:13:52,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That means Kubo Eiji made
 a mistake in building his strategy.</b></font>

146
00:13:52,664 --> 00:13:55,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Something else has happened behind the scenes.</b></font>

147
00:13:57,314 --> 00:13:58,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Something else...</b></font>

148
00:14:01,744 --> 00:14:02,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What did you say?</b></font>

149
00:14:02,914 --> 00:14:06,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's ridiculous!
Do you have the section time?</b></font>

150
00:14:06,414 --> 00:14:07,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes.</b></font>

151
00:14:08,744 --> 00:14:09,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's</b></font>

152
00:14:11,114 --> 00:14:12,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>impossible.</b></font>

153
00:14:12,564 --> 00:14:16,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That FD isn't built to
match such a high pace.</b></font>

154
00:14:17,874 --> 00:14:20,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Was there a miscalculation?</b></font>

155
00:14:20,314 --> 00:14:23,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, that can't be the case.</b></font>

156
00:14:23,314 --> 00:14:26,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The FD3S shouldn't have that kind of potential.</b></font>

157
00:14:28,264 --> 00:14:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dammit!</b></font>

158
00:14:55,134 --> 00:14:58,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, what's happening?</b></font>

159
00:14:58,214 --> 00:15:01,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was on a roll when I went flat out.</b></font>

160
00:15:01,714 --> 00:15:03,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know I was.</b></font>

161
00:15:04,494 --> 00:15:06,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So why are you still there?</b></font>

162
00:15:08,524 --> 00:15:11,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why are you putting pressure on me,
 instead of falling behind?</b></font>

163
00:15:14,174 --> 00:15:22,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sidewinder tried to dominate us in intelligence gathering by dispatching scout teams since our first race in Kanagawa.</b></font>

164
00:15:22,914 --> 00:15:29,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Seasoned strategist Kubo's plan
 didn't work, probably because</b></font>

165
00:15:29,514 --> 00:15:40,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke's skills, that are refined by his peculiar daily training, greatly exceeded Kubo's expectations.</b></font>

166
00:15:41,164 --> 00:15:45,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The type of driving sense he's acquired becomes useful in many ways.</b></font>

167
00:15:46,324 --> 00:15:49,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if you don't control
 your car at full throttle</b></font>

168
00:15:49,664 --> 00:15:53,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you can understand how the car 
will behave at its max acceleration.</b></font>

169
00:15:53,714 --> 00:15:59,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Around the time when we began our Kanagawa races, Keisuke stopped practicing a flat out run.</b></font>

170
00:15:59,924 --> 00:16:03,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can lean more that way.</b></font>

171
00:16:03,154 --> 00:16:07,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And more than anything, you can finish your 
car's settings because of improved efficiency.</b></font>

172
00:16:07,564 --> 00:16:09,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. That makes sense.</b></font>

173
00:16:10,584 --> 00:16:18,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our opponent has a data analysis expert who can see through any imperfect camouflage.</b></font>

174
00:16:18,374 --> 00:16:21,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By focusing on the critical attacking areas, and going easy on the rest</b></font>

175
00:16:21,924 --> 00:16:28,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we created an evened out pace, which should have 
made it difficult for our opponent to gauge our potential.</b></font>

176
00:16:30,464 --> 00:16:34,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On top of that, Keisuke drives extremely fast even when he takes it easy.</b></font>

177
00:16:34,304 --> 00:16:40,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even Kubo couldn't anticipate a driver, who's 
trained on public roads, could pull such a stunt.</b></font>

178
00:16:42,014 --> 00:16:44,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's beyond my imagination.</b></font>

179
00:16:44,374 --> 00:16:48,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They may have figured out 
how we control our cars</b></font>

180
00:16:48,164 --> 00:16:52,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but we didn't give them any information
 about our peak performance.</b></font>

181
00:16:52,414 --> 00:16:54,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This battle of intelligence is even.</b></font>

182
00:16:55,014 --> 00:16:57,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke is amazing.</b></font>

183
00:17:10,234 --> 00:17:12,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, I got it.</b></font>

184
00:17:13,214 --> 00:17:18,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The first hill climb is over, and the
 result is not what we expected.</b></font>

185
00:17:18,664 --> 00:17:23,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He failed to outrun him, which means the
game is carried over to the second run, right?</b></font>

186
00:17:23,734 --> 00:17:24,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

187
00:17:26,414 --> 00:17:28,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the way it should be.</b></font>

188
00:17:28,114 --> 00:17:32,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bet his brain is 
frozen like a glacier.</b></font>

189
00:17:34,374 --> 00:17:36,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But he has time to recover.</b></font>

190
00:17:36,914 --> 00:17:41,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'll do better without annoying 
restraints, like strategies or pride.</b></font>

191
00:17:42,944 --> 00:17:45,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. 
I know what you mean.</b></font>

192
00:17:45,864 --> 00:17:49,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Something inside him
has to be awakened.</b></font>

193
00:17:49,364 --> 00:17:52,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's all he needs in a game
of tag on a mountain pass.</b></font>

194
00:17:54,174 --> 00:17:55,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Remember the basics.</b></font>

195
00:17:56,664 --> 00:18:01,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A battle tends to be settled
by something very simple.</b></font>

196
00:18:12,794 --> 00:18:14,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm very sorry.</b></font>

197
00:18:14,524 --> 00:18:19,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't have to apologize. 
The car is in great condition.</b></font>

198
00:18:19,354 --> 00:18:22,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My instinct tells me that
I had a pretty good time.</b></font>

199
00:18:22,914 --> 00:18:24,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Am I wrong?</b></font>

200
00:18:24,214 --> 00:18:26,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're exactly right.</b></font>

201
00:18:26,314 --> 00:18:30,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You beat your own
section 4 record by 2 seconds.</b></font>

202
00:18:31,714 --> 00:18:32,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See?</b></font>

203
00:18:32,864 --> 00:18:34,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I had good feedback.</b></font>

204
00:18:34,664 --> 00:18:36,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not like I lost.</b></font>

205
00:18:36,474 --> 00:18:39,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm struggling a little,
but I'll recover from here.</b></font>

206
00:18:40,564 --> 00:18:43,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got to pull myself together.</b></font>

207
00:18:51,224 --> 00:18:52,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ready to go, Keisuke?</b></font>

208
00:18:52,984 --> 00:18:57,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anytime. I'll throw everything
I've got into this second run.</b></font>

209
00:18:57,044 --> 00:18:59,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If this drags on into a
third run, I'll definitely lose.</b></font>

210
00:19:00,654 --> 00:19:04,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You look like you're enjoying this, despite your desperate comment.</b></font>

211
00:19:05,614 --> 00:19:10,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm enjoying this from
the bottom of my heart.</b></font>

212
00:19:10,034 --> 00:19:14,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This could be my happiest 
moment since Project D began.</b></font>

213
00:19:26,794 --> 00:19:27,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's begin!</b></font>

214
00:19:28,624 --> 00:19:30,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five seconds till start!</b></font>

215
00:19:30,474 --> 00:19:31,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Four</b></font>

216
00:19:31,524 --> 00:19:32,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Three</b></font>

217
00:19:32,544 --> 00:19:33,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Two</b></font>

218
00:19:33,754 --> 00:19:34,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One</b></font>

219
00:19:34,614 --> 00:19:35,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

220
00:19:46,324 --> 00:19:49,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There won't be a third run. 
If there is, you'll lose.</b></font>

221
00:19:50,344 --> 00:19:53,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In any case, I'm proud of 
what you've achieved, Keisuke.</b></font>

222
00:20:22,894 --> 00:20:26,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is breathtaking, isn't it?</b></font>

223
00:20:26,014 --> 00:20:29,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He was at a disadvantage in every aspect.</b></font>

224
00:20:29,314 --> 00:20:34,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takahashi Keisuke was an incredible street racer even back then</b></font>

225
00:20:34,174 --> 00:20:37,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but he turned out to be even
better than we imagined.</b></font>

226
00:20:37,244 --> 00:20:38,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right.</b></font>

227
00:20:38,664 --> 00:20:43,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like I said, Project D's double 
aces won't lose no matter what.</b></font>

228
00:20:43,784 --> 00:20:51,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But turbo charged cars tend to lose
 power over time because of heat soak.</b></font>

229
00:20:51,244 --> 00:20:56,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A longer race will negatively affect the FD.</b></font>

230
00:20:56,104 --> 00:20:59,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takahashi Keisuke should know
that better than anyone else.</b></font>

231
00:20:59,704 --> 00:21:05,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know where, but he'll make a spurt in the second half of the race.</b></font>

232
00:21:05,054 --> 00:21:05,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I agree.</b></font>

233
00:21:09,374 --> 00:21:10,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here they come!</b></font>

234
00:21:18,344 --> 00:21:25,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going to get a kick out of Takahashi Keisuke's cannonball dash which has beaten a number of tough challengers.</b></font>

235
00:21:28,374 --> 00:21:31,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's going to be epic in this final stage.</b></font>

236
00:21:34,334 --> 00:21:39,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't imagine what's gonna happen, or how the race will turn out.</b></font>

237
00:21:39,074 --> 00:21:44,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, both drivers are putting
their lives on the line to drive so fast.</b></font>

238
00:22:00,874 --> 00:22:05,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's making it obvious that he's just cruising. He's not pushing it to the limit.</b></font>

239
00:22:06,914 --> 00:22:09,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even so, he's still fast, and
maintaining a high speed pace.</b></font>

240
00:22:12,214 --> 00:22:13,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nice execution.</b></font>

241
00:22:14,264 --> 00:22:17,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't expect him to be
able to pull off such a move.</b></font>

242
00:22:17,314 --> 00:22:20,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't realize he was so 
skillful until I drove behind him.
</b></font>

243
00:22:21,794 --> 00:22:27,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That aside, his car seems so fun to drive.</b></font>

244
00:22:27,034 --> 00:22:32,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's quite shocking to see a driver who can compete at this high of a level.</b></font>

245
00:22:35,954 --> 00:22:40,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Has my NSX ever looked
like that from the outside?</b></font>

246
00:22:45,374 --> 00:22:46,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm being sucked in...</b></font>

247
00:22:49,214 --> 00:22:53,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm being sucked in 
by this pleasant rhythm</b></font>

248
00:22:53,424 --> 00:22:55,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and getting synchronized.</b></font>

249
00:23:05,464 --> 00:23:08,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just don't get it.</b></font>

250
00:23:08,004 --> 00:23:12,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There are many FD3S's at time attack events between tuning shops.</b></font>

251
00:23:12,214 --> 00:23:17,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've seen many time attack specialty 
FDs that looked like race cars.</b></font>

252
00:23:17,984 --> 00:23:22,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought I was well aware of that particular FD's strengths and weaknesses.</b></font>

253
00:23:22,944 --> 00:23:27,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was confident that we'd
built a victory worthy NSX.</b></font>

254
00:23:27,214 --> 00:23:29,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't understand this.</b></font>

255
00:23:29,704 --> 00:23:31,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you think, Mr. Kubo?</b></font>

256
00:23:32,374 --> 00:23:35,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can never be certain about
the outcome of a competition.</b></font>

257
00:23:35,704 --> 00:23:42,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We were outsmarted in data collection, but it's still within our expectations.</b></font>

258
00:23:42,444 --> 00:23:48,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We ran our simulation with a reasonable margin, just in case. We're not stupid.</b></font>

259
00:23:50,064 --> 00:23:56,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe not by 15 seconds, but our
car still has an absolute advantage.</b></font>

260
00:23:56,344 --> 00:24:00,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, unlike circuits, unexpected things happen on mountain passes.</b></font>

261
00:24:00,344 --> 00:24:06,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So far, our opponent is doing an excellent job.</b></font>

262
00:24:06,374 --> 00:24:07,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We haven't lost yet.</b></font>

263
00:24:07,964 --> 00:24:11,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This time, our leader will
turn the situation around.</b></font>

264
00:24:11,724 --> 00:24:15,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he can manage this second run, there'll be no reason for us to lose.</b></font>

265
00:24:15,264 --> 00:24:17,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing can shake our absolute advantage.</b></font>

266
00:24:23,714 --> 00:24:26,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This pleasant feeling will 
eventually come to an end.</b></font>

267
00:24:28,944 --> 00:24:31,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There'll be a moment when
it will switch to combat mode.</b></font>

268
00:24:32,784 --> 00:24:37,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'll make a full throttle dash
like I did in the first run.</b></font>

269
00:24:38,924 --> 00:24:44,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If my NSX and I can't keep up 
with it, this battle will be over.</b></font>

270
00:24:48,414 --> 00:24:50,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where? Where are you
going to make your move?</b></font>

271
00:25:39,014 --> 00:25:44,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even when night falls, the scenery remains unchanged.</b></font>

272
00:25:44,014 --> 00:25:48,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Looking back at the path I've taken.</b></font>

273
00:25:48,904 --> 00:25:53,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sadness, happiness, incurable pains.</b></font>

274
00:25:53,414 --> 00:26:03,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Realizing that there are too many to count, as I walk alone.</b></font>

275
00:25:59,214 --> 00:26:01,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Countless number of memorable scenes.</b></font>

276
00:26:01,754 --> 00:26:04,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We lived through the hustle and bustle.</b></font>

277
00:26:04,154 --> 00:26:06,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sometimes we argued, sometimes we understood.</b></font>

278
00:26:06,494 --> 00:26:09,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It wasn't always pretty, but I keep the truth to myself</b></font>

279
00:26:09,294 --> 00:26:12,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as I take a new step.</b></font>

280
00:26:12,224 --> 00:26:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rosy clouds embellish the city.</b></font>

281
00:26:16,974 --> 00:26:23,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I quietly ask about my future.</b></font>

282
00:26:23,004 --> 00:26:26,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The sky remains silent.</b></font>

283
00:26:26,774 --> 00:26:36,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Only illuminating this path before me.</b></font>

284
00:26:36,114 --> 00:26:38,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Feel the translucent scenery.</b></font>

285
00:26:40,944 --> 00:26:43,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The setting sun plays a melody.</b></font>

286
00:26:45,824 --> 00:26:48,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Feel the translucent scenery.</b></font>

287
00:26:50,674 --> 00:26:52,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The setting sun plays a melody.</b></font>

